Invocation Name: popular cocktails
des:
Whether you are planning a party or simply wondering what to order during your next night out on the town, you should review a list of popular cocktails (content provided by Karen Frazier). Popular Cocktails tells you all about this list. 

Start the skill by saying 

"Alexa, Open Popular Cocktails"

It will give you a random cocktail drink and what it is made of, not ranked by popularity.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
